name: Openstreetmap, Baden-wuerttemberg Buildings, Germany, 2008
description: This data came from openstreetmaps and shows various building polygons throughout the Baden-wuerttemberg administrative area in Germany. Building data is incomplete but does show detailed information about the locations of various buildings, including attributes for building name when available.
